msgid "We need to install the required package at first:"
msgstr "We need to install the required package at first:"

#: ../../source/techniques/caching.rst:18
msgid "In-memory cache"
msgstr "In-memory cache"

#: ../../source/techniques/caching.rst:20
msgid ""
"Nest provides a unified API for various cache storage providers. The "
"built-in one is an in-memory data store. However, you can easily switch "
"to a more comprehensive solution, like Redis. In order to enable caching,"
" firstly import ``CacheModule`` and call its ``register()`` method."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/techniques/caching.rst:37
msgid "Then just tie ``CacheInterceptor`` somewhere."
msgstr "Then just tie ``CacheInterceptor`` somewhere."

