msgstr "Repository pattern"

#: ../../source/techniques/sql.rst:112
msgid ""
"The `TypeORM <https://github.com/typeorm/typeorm>`__ supports the "
"repository design pattern, so each entity has its own Repository. These "
"repositories can be obtained from the database connection."
msgstr ""

