"The ``Photo`` entity belongs to the ``photo`` directory. This directory "
"represents the ``PhotoModule``. It’s your decision where you gonna keep "
"your model files. From our point of view, the best way’s to hold them "
"nearly their **domain**, in the corresponding module directory."
msgstr ""

