msgid ""
"In order to create your custom repository, use ``@EntityRepository()`` "
"decorator and extend ``Repository`` class."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/techniques/sql.rst:350
msgid ""
"info **Hint** Both ``@EntityRepository()`` and ``Repository`` are exposed"
" from ``typeorm`` package."
msgstr ""

